OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775426988
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter victim seriously injured in
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FA 24-year-old man has been charged
OL,8,Fwith attempted murder after a man was
OL,9,Fshot in Bristol earlier this week.
OL,11,FWilliam Scammell, from Speedwell, has
OL,12,Falso been charged with being in
OL,13,Fpossession of a shortened shotgun.
OL,15,FThe gun was fired at a car in
OL,16,FSpeedwell Road at around 1.50pm on
OL,17,FWednesday 1 April. The victim, a man
OL,18,Fin his twenties, remains in hospital
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
