PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775426988
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter victim seriously injured in
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FScammell was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder just after 2.30am on
OL,9,FThursday, 2 April.
OL,11,FAnother man and a woman, also both in
OL,12,Ftheir twenties, were arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender
OL,14,Fafter the incident. They have since
OL,15,Fbeen released on police bail.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
