OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775426988
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter victim seriously injured in
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FSenior investigating officer Det Ch
OL,8,FInsp Jess Aston said: "We understand
OL,9,Fthis has been a very shocking and
OL,10,Fconcerning incident, but we would like
OL,11,Fto reassure the public that this
OL,12,Fremains a priority investigation for
OL,13,Fus.
OL,15,F"Neighbourhood officers continue to
OL,16,Fconduct high-visibility reassurance
OL,17,Fpatrols in the area and anyone with
OL,18,Fany concerns or questions are
OL,19,Fencouraged to speak with us."
